adminkit (0.13) unstable; urgency=low

  * added -s option to output messages to syslog.
  * added -n option to not launch commands during run.
  * added the activate_service and deactivate_service role commands.
  * fixed files_to_command.
  * allow to customize locations with /etc/update-adminkit.conf.
  * allow add_var to be a nested name.

 -- Frederic Lepied <flepied@gmail.com>  Mon, 03 Oct 2011 22:14:57 +0100

